    "body": "Those are peer dependencies, not dev dependencies. A peer dependency is something that has to be installed _along_ with the package. If you are using npm 7 or later, these are installed automatically. If you are using yarn or an older version of npm, then you'll need to manually install them. We recommend using a recent version of npm to avoid having to do that.",
